                     <interp inst="t17290116-8-person63" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , and the Prosecutor confessing he was but a Lodger in the House of Mrs. Williams, the Jury found her <rs id="t17290116-8-verdict32" type="verdictDescription">
